description.en: OxyDev Network aims to build a cross-chain and cross-platform content value asset network, based on BaaS, Visual open cloud platform, API & SDK, smart contract group, hybrid Oracle engine and other technologies, through the use of The power of Polkadot SubstateFramework on the open network provides global users/creators with integrated subscription management services, content copyright confirmation, content digital asset distribution (STO-NFT), content creation incentives, advertising incentives and other services.
